              <div class="bouton-review"><a href="#">Read more</a></div>
              <p>De<a href="#">Dylan</a> Le 20/09/2023</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="review-content">
          <img src="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ANu6ZedIfA4/maxresdefault.jpg" alt="Review Image" class="review-image">
          <div class="review-text">
            <h2>Call of Duty: Vanguard</h2>
            <p>"Call of Duty: Vanguard" brings fast-paced action and stunning visuals, though the campaign lacks emotional depth. The multiplayer shines with diverse modes and the new "Champion Hill" feature, offering a fresh twist to the gameplay. A solid but not groundbreaking entry in the series.</p>
            <div class="review-container-text">
              <div class="bouton-review"><a href="#">Read more</a></div>
              <p>De<a href="#">Dylan</a> Le 20/09/2023</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <button class="prev">←</button>
      <button class="next">→</button>
    </section>

    <!-- ------------------------------------------------------ -->
    <!-- ------------------- Séparateur ----------------------- -->
    
    <div class="separator">
      <span>CONCTACT US</span>
    </div>

    <!-- ------------------------------------------------------ -->
    <!-- ------------------- contact ----------------------- -->

    <section class="contact-section">
      <div class="contact-container">
        <form class="contact-form" action="#" method="post">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="name">Your Name:</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" class="form-input" placeholder="Enter your name" required>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">Your Email:</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" class="form-input" placeholder="Enter your email" required>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="message">Your Message:</label>
            <textarea id="message" class="form-textarea" rows="5" placeholder="Type your message here..." required></textarea>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="contact-btn">Send Message</button>
        </form>
      <div>
    </section>


</main




{% endblock %}
